                "text": "JWT claims validation is explicitly disabled via jwt.WithoutClaimsValidation().\nThis bypasses expiry (exp), not-before (nbf), and issued-at (iat) checks.\nExpired or future tokens will be accepted as valid. Remove this option.\n"
